---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import T from '../../components/T.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="體態管理計算機 · Body Composition Calculator — Matt Ye"
  description="以台灣國人膳食營養素參考攝取量（DRIs）第八版與國際運動營養學會（ISSN）、ACSM 文獻為基礎的 BMR / TDEE / 巨量營養素與碳循環計算工具。純前端計算，資料不上傳、不儲存。"
>
  <div class="container-wide calc-page">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="calc-hero">
      <h1><T zh="體態管理" en="Body Composition" /> <span class="accent-text"><T zh="計算機" en="Calculator" /></span></h1>
      <p class="calc-subtitle">
        <T zh="依據台灣「國人膳食營養素參考攝取量」第八版（DRIs）與國際運動營養學會（ISSN）、美國運動醫學會（ACSM）等文獻，估算你的 BMR、TDEE、每日巨量營養素目標，並規劃碳循環週菜單。" en="Estimate your BMR, TDEE, and daily macronutrient targets, and plan a weekly carb-cycling menu — grounded in Taiwan's Dietary Reference Intakes (DRIs, 8th ed.), the ISSN, and ACSM literature." />
      </p>
      <p class="calc-privacy">🔒 <T zh="所有計算都在你的瀏覽器內完成，資料不會上傳或儲存到任何伺服器。" en="All calculations run entirely in your browser — nothing is uploaded or stored on any server." /></p>
    </section>

    <!-- Disclaimer -->
    <section class="calc-disclaimer">
      <p><strong><T zh="⚠️ 重要提醒：" en="⚠️ Important: " /></strong><T zh="本工具僅供健康成人的自我管理參考，並非醫療建議，不能取代醫師或營養師的專業判斷。" en="This tool is for self-management reference by healthy adults only. It is not medical advice and cannot replace the professional judgment of a physician or dietitian." /></p>
      <ul>
        <li><T zh="孕婦、哺乳婦：每日醣類攝取不建議低於 175 公克，請勿自行嘗試低碳/碳循環飲食。" en="Pregnant or breastfeeding women: daily carbohydrate intake should not fall below 175 g; do not attempt low-carb or carb-cycling diets on your own." /></li>
        <li><T zh="糖尿病或血糖異常者：碳循環的每日醣類變化幅度大，可能造成血糖波動，請先諮詢醫師。" en="People with diabetes or blood-sugar issues: carb cycling's large daily carbohydrate swings can cause blood-sugar fluctuations — consult your physician first." /></li>
        <li><T zh="有飲食失調（厭食、暴食）病史者：不建議在無專業協助下使用熱量赤字或碳循環策略。" en="People with a history of eating disorders (anorexia, bulimia): using calorie-deficit or carb-cycling strategies without professional support is not recommended." /></li>
        <li><T zh="本工具的 ACSM 風險評估為中高風險者，建議先諮詢醫師再開始運動計畫或大幅熱量調整。" en="If the ACSM screening rates you medium-to-high risk, consult a physician before starting an exercise program or making large calorie adjustments." /></li>
        <li><T zh="有慢性腎臟病（CKD）或其他肝、腎代謝疾病者：請勿使用本工具估算你的蛋白質攝取量，本工具部分選項（如減脂期 g/kg 建議值）對腎臟負擔較大，可能造成危險。蛋白質代謝會產生含氮廢物，過量攝取會加重肝、腎處理負擔。請諮詢醫師／營養師，依你的血清尿素氮（BUN）、腎臟過濾率（eGFR）、GOT、GPT 等檢驗數值，計算適合你的攝取量。" en="People with chronic kidney disease (CKD) or other liver/kidney metabolic conditions: do NOT use this tool to estimate your protein intake. Some options (e.g. the cutting-phase g/kg values) place a heavier load on the kidneys and may be dangerous. Protein metabolism produces nitrogenous waste, and excess intake burdens the liver and kidneys. Consult a physician/dietitian and calculate an intake suited to you based on your BUN, eGFR, GOT, and GPT test values." /></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Input form -->
    <section class="calc-section">
      <p class="section-heading">1. <T zh="輸入基本資料" en="Enter Your Details" /></p>
      <div class="calc-form-card">
        <div class="form-grid">
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="生理性別" en="Sex" /></span>
            <select id="in-sex">
              <option value="male" data-zh="男性" data-en="Male">男性</option>
              <option value="female" data-zh="女性" data-en="Female">女性</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="年齡" en="Age (years)" /></span>
            <input type="number" id="in-age" value="30" min="15" max="100" step="1" />
          </label>
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="體重（公斤）" en="Weight (kg)" /></span>
            <input type="number" id="in-weight" value="70" min="30" max="250" step="0.1" />
          </label>
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="身高（公分）" en="Height (cm)" /></span>
            <input type="number" id="in-height" value="170" min="120" max="220" step="0.1" />
          </label>
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="體脂率（選填）" en="Body fat % (optional)" /></span>
            <input type="number" id="in-bfr" placeholder="e.g. 25" min="3" max="70" step="0.1" />
          </label>
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="目標體重（公斤）" en="Target weight (kg)" /></span>
            <input type="number" id="in-target" value="65" min="30" max="250" step="0.1" />
          </label>
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="活動量" en="Activity level" /></span>
            <select id="in-pal">
              <option value="1.2" data-zh="久坐（幾乎不運動）" data-en="Sedentary (little/no exercise)">久坐（幾乎不運動）</option>
              <option value="1.375" data-zh="輕度活動（每週運動 1–3 次）" data-en="Light (1–3×/week)">輕度活動（每週運動 1–3 次）</option>
              <option value="1.55" selected data-zh="中度活動（每週運動 3–5 次）" data-en="Moderate (3–5×/week)">中度活動（每週運動 3–5 次）</option>
              <option value="1.725" data-zh="高度活動（每週運動 6–7 次）" data-en="Active (6–7×/week)">高度活動（每週運動 6–7 次）</option>
              <option value="1.9" data-zh="極高強度（勞力工作／每日訓練）" data-en="Athlete (physical job / daily training)">極高強度（勞力工作／每日訓練）</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="目標" en="Goal" /></span>
            <select id="in-goal">
              <option value="bulk_high" data-zh="增肌增重（TDEE +20% 或 +500kcal）" data-en="Bulk (TDEE +20% or +500 kcal)">增肌增重（TDEE +20% 或 +500kcal）</option>
              <option value="bulk_low" data-zh="增肌增重（TDEE +10% 或 +200kcal）" data-en="Bulk (TDEE +10% or +200 kcal)">增肌增重（TDEE +10% 或 +200kcal）</option>
              <option value="maintain" selected data-zh="維持體態（100% TDEE）" data-en="Maintain (100% TDEE)">維持體態（100% TDEE）</option>
              <option value="cut_low" data-zh="減脂減重（TDEE -10% 或 -200kcal）" data-en="Cut (TDEE −10% or −200 kcal)">減脂減重（TDEE -10% 或 -200kcal）</option>
              <option value="cut_high" data-zh="減脂減重（TDEE -20% 或 -500kcal）" data-en="Cut (TDEE −20% or −500 kcal)">減脂減重（TDEE -20% 或 -500kcal）</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="蛋白質攝取量（g/kg/day）" en="Protein intake (g/kg/day)" /></span>
            <select id="in-protein-gkg">
              <option value="1.1" data-zh="1.1 g/kg — 一般成人（台灣 DRIs RDA，無特別運動需求）" data-en="1.1 g/kg — general adults (Taiwan DRIs RDA, no special training)">1.1 g/kg — 一般成人（台灣 DRIs RDA，無特別運動需求）</option>
              <option value="1.2" data-zh="1.2 g/kg — 70 歲以上高齡者（台灣 DRIs 建議）" data-en="1.2 g/kg — older adults 70+ (Taiwan DRIs)">1.2 g/kg — 70 歲以上高齡者（台灣 DRIs 建議）</option>
              <option value="1.4" data-zh="1.4 g/kg — 開始運動／輕度訓練族群（ISSN 下限）" data-en="1.4 g/kg — beginners / light training (ISSN lower bound)">1.4 g/kg — 開始運動／輕度訓練族群（ISSN 下限）</option>
              <option value="1.6" selected data-zh="1.6 g/kg — 規律阻力訓練、維持體態" data-en="1.6 g/kg — regular resistance training, maintenance">1.6 g/kg — 規律阻力訓練、維持體態</option>
              <option value="1.8" data-zh="1.8 g/kg — 增肌訓練族群" data-en="1.8 g/kg — muscle-building training">1.8 g/kg — 增肌訓練族群</option>
              <option value="2.0" data-zh="2.0 g/kg — 高強度訓練（ISSN 一般上限）" data-en="2.0 g/kg — high-intensity training (ISSN upper bound)">2.0 g/kg — 高強度訓練（ISSN 一般上限）</option>
              <option value="2.3" data-zh="2.3 g/kg — 減脂期保留肌肉量（ISSN 下限）" data-en="2.3 g/kg — cutting, muscle retention (ISSN lower)">2.3 g/kg — 減脂期保留肌肉量（ISSN 下限）</option>
              <option value="2.4" data-zh="2.4 g/kg — 減脂期保留肌肉量（中）" data-en="2.4 g/kg — cutting, muscle retention (mid)">2.4 g/kg — 減脂期保留肌肉量（中）</option>
              <option value="3.1" data-zh="3.1 g/kg — 積極減脂／高強度保留肌肉量（ISSN 上限）" data-en="3.1 g/kg — aggressive cut / max retention (ISSN upper)">3.1 g/kg — 積極減脂／高強度保留肌肉量（ISSN 上限）</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="form-field">
            <span><T zh="飲食規劃類型" en="Diet type" /></span>
            <select id="in-diettype">
              <option value="baseline" data-zh="一般飲食（Baseline）" data-en="General (Baseline)">一般飲食（Baseline）</option>
              <option value="balanced" data-zh="均衡飲食" data-en="Balanced">均衡飲食</option>
              <option value="dash" data-zh="得舒飲食 DASH Diet" data-en="DASH Diet">得舒飲食 DASH Diet</option>
              <option value="zone" data-zh="區域飲食 Zone Diet" data-en="Zone Diet">區域飲食 Zone Diet</option>
              <option value="modlowcarb" selected data-zh="中度低醣飲食" data-en="Moderate low-carb">中度低醣飲食</option>
              <option value="lowcarb" data-zh="低醣飲食" data-en="Low-carb">低醣飲食</option>
              <option value="verylowcarb" data-zh="極低醣" data-en="Very low-carb">極低醣</option>
              <option value="verylowcarbketo" data-zh="極低醣＋生酮" data-en="Very low-carb + keto">極低醣＋生酮</option>
              <option value="keto" data-zh="生酮飲食 Keto Diet" data-en="Keto Diet">生酮飲食 Keto Diet</option>
              <option value="highcarb" data-zh="高碳飲食" data-en="High-carb">高碳飲食</option>
              <option value="carbcycle" data-zh="碳循環飲食（Carb Cycling）" data-en="Carb Cycling">碳循環飲食（Carb Cycling）</option>
            </select>
          </label>
        </div>
        <p class="form-hint" id="diettype-hint"></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ACSM risk screening -->
    <section class="calc-section">
      <p class="section-heading">2. <T zh="ACSM 運動健康風險評估" en="ACSM Exercise Health-Risk Screening" /></p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc"><T zh="美國運動醫學會（ACSM）建議開始運動計畫前的自我篩檢，勾選符合你狀況的項目。" en="A self-screen recommended by the American College of Sports Medicine (ACSM) before starting an exercise program. Check any items that apply to you." /></p>
      <div class="acsm-list" id="acsm-list">
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="1" /> <T zh="年齡：男性 ≥ 45 歲 / 女性 ≥ 55 歲" en="Age: male ≥ 45 / female ≥ 55" /></label>
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="1" /> <T zh="家族史：父親 55 歲前或母親 65 歲前出現心臟、肝臟或代謝疾病" en="Family history: heart, liver, or metabolic disease in father before 55 or mother before 65" /></label>
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="1" /> <T zh="吸菸：有吸菸習慣或戒菸未滿六個月，或長期暴露於二手菸" en="Smoking: current smoker, quit within 6 months, or long-term secondhand-smoke exposure" /></label>
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="1" /> <T zh="近三個月內，未參與每週至少三天的中等強度運動" en="In the past 3 months, not doing moderate exercise at least 3 days/week" /></label>
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="1" /> <T zh="肥胖：BMI ≥ 30，或男性腰圍 ≥ 102cm／女性腰圍 ≥ 88cm" en="Obesity: BMI ≥ 30, or waist ≥ 102 cm (male) / ≥ 88 cm (female)" /></label>
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="1" /> <T zh="高血壓：收縮壓 ≥ 140 mmHg 或舒張壓 ≥ 90 mmHg，或正在服用降血壓藥物" en="Hypertension: systolic ≥ 140 or diastolic ≥ 90 mmHg, or taking BP medication" /></label>
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="1" /> <T zh="血脂異常：LDL ≥ 130、總膽固醇 ≥ 200 mg/dL，或正在服用降血脂藥物" en="Dyslipidemia: LDL ≥ 130 or total cholesterol ≥ 200 mg/dL, or taking lipid-lowering medication" /></label>
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="1" /> <T zh="糖尿病前期：空腹血糖 ≥ 100 mg/dL" en="Pre-diabetes: fasting glucose ≥ 100 mg/dL" /></label>
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="-1" /> <T zh="HDL（高密度膽固醇）大於 60 mg/dL（保護因子，可抵銷 1 項風險）" en="HDL (good cholesterol) above 60 mg/dL (protective factor — offsets 1 risk)" /></label>
        <label class="acsm-item"><input type="checkbox" data-acsm="1" /> <T zh="本人已確診心臟、肝臟或肺部疾病" en="You have a diagnosed heart, liver, or lung disease" /></label>
      </div>
      <div class="acsm-result" id="acsm-result"><T zh="請勾選以上項目查看風險評估結果" en="Check the items above to see your risk assessment." /></div>
    </section>

    <!-- BMR/TDEE results -->
    <section class="calc-section">
      <p class="section-heading">3. <T zh="BMR / TDEE 估算結果" en="BMR / TDEE Estimates" /></p>
      <div class="calc-bento stat-list">
        <div class="stat-row">
          <div class="stat-row-label">
            <div class="stat-row-title">BMR (Mifflin-St Jeor)</div>
            <div class="stat-row-sub"><T zh="主要採用值，文獻實證最準確" en="Primary value — most accurate per literature" /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row-num" id="out-bmr-mifflin">—</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-row">
          <div class="stat-row-label">
            <div class="stat-row-title">BMR (Katch-McArdle)</div>
            <div class="stat-row-sub" id="katch-sub"><T zh="需輸入體脂率" en="Requires body fat %" /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row-num" id="out-bmr-katch">—</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-row">
          <div class="stat-row-label">
            <div class="stat-row-title">BMR (Harris-Benedict)</div>
            <div class="stat-row-sub"><T zh="僅供參考，易高估" en="Reference only — tends to overestimate" /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row-num" id="out-bmr-hb">—</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-row">
          <div class="stat-row-label">
            <div class="stat-row-title"><T zh="TDEE（每日總消耗）" en="TDEE (total daily expenditure)" /></div>
            <div class="stat-row-sub"><T zh="BMR（Mifflin）× 活動量倍率" en="BMR (Mifflin) × activity multiplier" /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row-num" id="out-tdee">—</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-row">
          <div class="stat-row-label">
            <div class="stat-row-title"><T zh="目標每日攝取熱量" en="Target daily calorie intake" /></div>
            <div class="stat-row-sub" id="target-kcal-sub">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row-num" id="out-target-kcal">—</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-row">
          <div class="stat-row-label">
            <div class="stat-row-title"><T zh="預估達標天數" en="Estimated days to goal" /></div>
            <div class="stat-row-sub"><T zh="以 7700 kcal ≈ 1kg 換算" en="Based on 7700 kcal ≈ 1 kg" /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row-num" id="out-days">—</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="calc-feasibility" id="feasibility-msg"></p>
    </section>

    <!-- Macro targets + weekly training schedule (merged) -->
    <section class="calc-section">
      <p class="section-heading">4. <T zh="每日巨量營養素目標" en="Daily Macronutrient Targets" /></p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc">
        <T zh="蛋白質採「體重 × 每公斤克數」計算（ISSN 2017 實證範圍），每日固定；碳水依下方每天的訓練強度逐日調整：一般飲食類型採 ACSM/AND/Dietitians of Canada 2016 聯合聲明的訓練量框架（依一般健身族群調整，非耐力運動員數值）；生酮／極低醣類飲食則改採「Targeted/Cyclical Ketogenic Diet」小幅碳水微調，避免破壞酮症；脂肪為每日剩餘熱量的彈性項。以下先顯示週平均，可在下方表格調整每天的訓練強度。" en="Protein is fixed daily, calculated as body weight × g/kg (ISSN 2017 evidence range). Carbs adjust per day by that day's training intensity: standard diets use the ACSM/AND/Dietitians of Canada 2016 joint-statement training-load framework (scaled for general trainees, not endurance athletes); keto / very-low-carb diets instead use a small Targeted/Cyclical Ketogenic Diet carb bump to avoid breaking ketosis. Fat is the flexible remainder of each day's calories. Weekly averages are shown below; adjust each day's training intensity in the table." />
      </p>
      <div class="stat-list" id="macro-grid">
        <div class="stat-row" data-macro="protein">
          <div class="stat-row-label">
            <div class="stat-row-title"><T zh="蛋白質" en="Protein" /> <span class="dri-badge" id="dri-protein">—</span></div>
            <div class="stat-row-sub" id="out-protein-detail">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row-num" id="out-protein-g">— g</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-row" data-macro="fat">
          <div class="stat-row-label">
            <div class="stat-row-title"><T zh="脂肪" en="Fat" /> <span class="dri-badge" id="dri-fat">—</span></div>
            <div class="stat-row-sub" id="out-fat-detail">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row-num" id="out-fat-g">— g</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-row" data-macro="carb">
          <div class="stat-row-label">
            <div class="stat-row-title"><T zh="碳水化合物" en="Carbohydrate" /> <span class="dri-badge" id="dri-carb">—</span></div>
            <div class="stat-row-sub" id="out-carb-detail">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row-num" id="out-carb-g">— g</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="dri-legend"><T zh="✅ 符合 DRIs 建議範圍 &nbsp;&nbsp; ⚠️ 超出 DRIs 一般建議範圍（特殊飲食型態，建議諮詢營養師）" en="✅ Within DRIs range &nbsp;&nbsp; ⚠️ Outside typical DRIs range (special dietary pattern — consult a dietitian)" /></p>

      <p class="week-grid-heading"><T zh="每日訓練強度與巨量營養素明細（選擇下方下拉選單即時更新）" en="Daily training intensity & macro breakdown (updates live as you change the dropdowns)" /></p>
      <div class="supp-table-wrap">
        <table class="supp-table week-detail-table">
          <thead><tr><th><T zh="星期" en="Day" /></th><th><T zh="訓練強度" en="Training" /></th><th><T zh="蛋白" en="Protein" /></th><th><T zh="碳水" en="Carb" /></th><th><T zh="脂肪" en="Fat" /></th></tr></thead>
          <tbody id="week-grid"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="calc-feasibility warn" id="cc-fat-warning" style="display:none"><T zh="⚠️ 在目前的熱量赤字與碳水設定下，部分日子的脂肪額度會被壓到很低（可能低於必需脂肪酸建議量）。可考慮放寬熱量赤字，或降低該日的訓練強度。" en="⚠️ At the current deficit and carb settings, some days' fat allowance is squeezed very low (possibly below the essential-fatty-acid recommendation). Consider easing the deficit or lowering that day's training intensity." /></p>
    </section>

    <!-- Food-group servings (六大類食物換算) -->
    <section class="calc-section">
      <p class="section-heading">5. <T zh="六大類食物份數建議" en="Food-Group Servings" /></p>

      <p class="calc-subheading">5a. <T zh="總食物採買量（週）" en="Total Weekly Shopping Amount" /></p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc">
        <T zh="依衛福部《每日飲食指南》官方代換系統，把上方的週平均巨量營養素換算成六大類食物份數，方便採買與備餐參考。蔬菜、水果、乳品採一般建議的基礎份數，其餘依你的蛋白質／脂肪／碳水目標分配。" en="Using the official food-exchange system from Taiwan HPA's Daily Dietary Guidelines, this converts the weekly-average macros above into servings of the six food groups for shopping and meal-prep. Vegetables, fruit, and dairy use standard baseline servings; the rest is allocated to your protein/fat/carb targets." />
      </p>
      <div class="stat-list" id="servings-grid"></div>
      <p class="calc-section-desc" id="servings-carb-delta" style="display:none"></p>

      <p class="calc-subheading">5b. <T zh="每日飲食規劃" en="Daily Meal Plan" /></p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc">
        <T zh="把第 4 節每天的巨量營養素平均分配到 2–4 餐。均分是依 ISSN 蛋白質時機建議（Kerksick et al. 2017；Areta et al. 2013 發現平均分配優於過於集中或過於分散的攝取模式）；2 餐版本對應 16:8 限時進食（Time-Restricted Eating）。" en="Splits each day's macros from §4 evenly across 2–4 meals. Even distribution follows ISSN protein-timing guidance (Kerksick et al. 2017; Areta et al. 2013 found even spacing beats overly concentrated or overly spread intake); the 2-meal option corresponds to 16:8 time-restricted eating." />
      </p>
      <label class="form-field meal-count-field">
        <span><T zh="每日餐數" en="Meals per day" /></span>
        <select id="in-mealcount">
          <option value="2" data-zh="2 餐（16:8 限時進食）" data-en="2 meals (16:8 time-restricted)">2 餐（16:8 限時進食）</option>
          <option value="3" selected data-zh="3 餐" data-en="3 meals">3 餐</option>
          <option value="4" data-zh="4 餐" data-en="4 meals">4 餐</option>
        </select>
      </label>
      <p class="calc-section-desc" id="mealplan-168-note" style="display:none">
        <T zh="16:8 建議：在 8 小時進食窗口內平均分配兩餐（例如 12:00 與 20:00）。研究顯示搭配阻力訓練與足夠蛋白質，16:8 可減少脂肪量且不影響肌肉量與肌力（Moro et al. 2016；2024 統合分析），但可能略微降低睪固酮／IGF-1（Moro et al. 2016）。孕婦、糖尿病／血糖藥物使用者、有飲食失調病史者、青少年不建議嘗試，請先諮詢醫師。" en="16:8 tip: spread the two meals evenly within an 8-hour eating window (e.g. 12:00 and 20:00). With resistance training and adequate protein, 16:8 can reduce fat mass without losing muscle or strength (Moro et al. 2016; 2024 meta-analysis), though it may slightly lower testosterone/IGF-1 (Moro et al. 2016). Not recommended for pregnant women, people on diabetes/blood-sugar medication, those with an eating-disorder history, or adolescents — consult a physician first." />
      </p>
      <div class="supp-table-wrap">
        <table class="supp-table" id="mealplan-table"></table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Eating out + whole food guidance -->
    <section class="calc-section">
      <p class="section-heading">6. <T zh="外食技巧與原型食物" en="Eating-Out Tips & Whole Foods" /></p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc">
        <T zh="以下為業界／營養師的實務共識整理，並非一手文獻回顧（跟本頁其他章節的 DRIs/ISSN/ACSM 引用等級不同），僅供參考。內容為靜態整理，未依你選擇的飲食類型或目標動態調整。" en="The following is practical consensus from dietitians/industry, not a primary-literature review (a different evidence tier from the DRIs/ISSN/ACSM citations elsewhere on this page) — for reference only. This content is static and does not adjust to your selected diet type or goal." />
      </p>

      <p class="calc-subheading"><T zh="依場景挑選" en="By venue" /></p>
      <div class="venue-grid">
        <div class="venue-card">
          <div class="venue-title">🏪 <T zh="便利商店" en="Convenience store (7-11 / FamilyMart)" /></div>
          <p><b><T zh="優先：" en="Pick: " /></b><T zh="舒肥雞胸、茶葉蛋、無糖豆漿、溫泉蛋沙拉、地瓜" en="sous-vide chicken breast, tea eggs, unsweetened soy milk, onsen-egg salad, sweet potato" /></p>
          <p><b><T zh="少選：" en="Limit: " /></b><T zh="含糖飲料、沙拉醬包、油炸品（奶油可頌、燒烤飯糰）" en="sugary drinks, dressing packets, fried items (butter croissants, grilled rice balls)" /></p>
        </div>
        <div class="venue-card">
          <div class="venue-title">🍱 <T zh="自助餐" en="Self-serve buffet (Taiwanese cafeteria)" /></div>
          <p><b><T zh="優先：" en="Pick: " /></b><T zh="清蒸／滷／涼拌（蒜泥白肉、清蒸鱈魚），2 份純蔬菜" en="steamed / braised / cold-tossed dishes (garlic pork, steamed cod), 2 servings of plain vegetables" /></p>
          <p><b><T zh="少選：" en="Limit: " /></b><T zh="糖醋排骨、勾芡類；飯減 1/3～1/2" en="sweet-and-sour pork, thick-starch-sauce dishes; cut rice by 1/3–1/2" /></p>
        </div>
        <div class="venue-card">
          <div class="venue-title">🌃 <T zh="夜市／小吃" en="Night market / street food" /></div>
          <p><b><T zh="優先：" en="Pick: " /></b><T zh="鹽水雞（雞胸）、蒸玉米、蒸地瓜" en="salted chicken (breast), steamed corn, steamed sweet potato" /></p>
          <p><b><T zh="少選：" en="Limit: " /></b><T zh="大腸包小腸（澱粉＋高脂雙重疊加）、羹湯／勾芡" en="sausage-in-rice (starch + high fat), thick starchy soups" /></p>
        </div>
        <div class="venue-card">
          <div class="venue-title">🍔 <T zh="連鎖速食" en="Fast-food chains" /></div>
          <p><b><T zh="優先：" en="Pick: " /></b><T zh="嫩煎雞腿堡／烤雞沙拉；去雞皮（約 40% 熱量在皮）" en="pan-grilled chicken burger / grilled-chicken salad; remove the skin (~40% of calories are in the skin)" /></p>
          <p><b><T zh="少選：" en="Limit: " /></b><T zh="薯條（換玉米湯／沙拉）、含糖汽水" en="fries (swap for corn soup / salad), sugary soda" /></p>
        </div>
        <div class="venue-card">
          <div class="venue-title">🧋 <T zh="手搖飲料" en="Hand-shaken drinks (bubble tea)" /></div>
          <p><T zh="700ml 全糖珍奶≈60g 糖，已超過 WHO 每日游離糖建議上限。台大研究：市售「無糖」飲料 55.6% 仍檢出糖分。純茶不加料最安全。" en="A 700 ml full-sugar pearl milk tea ≈ 60 g sugar — above the WHO daily free-sugar limit. An NTU study found 55.6% of drinks labeled 'sugar-free' still tested positive for sugar. Plain unsweetened tea is safest." /></p>
        </div>
        <div class="venue-card">
          <div class="venue-title">🍱 <T zh="辦公室便當" en="Office bento box" /></div>
          <p><b><T zh="公式：" en="Formula: " /></b><T zh="飯半碗～1 碗＋2–3 份蛋白質＋2–3 份蔬菜。烹調法排序：蒸／燙 &gt; 滷／烤 &gt; 煎／炒 &gt; 炸／糖醋。" en="½–1 bowl rice + 2–3 servings protein + 2–3 servings vegetables. Cooking-method ranking: steamed/blanched > braised/baked > pan-fried/stir-fried > deep-fried/sweet-and-sour." /></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="calc-subheading"><T zh="原型食物與烹飪方式" en="Whole foods & cooking methods" /></p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc">
        <T zh="原型食物指仍可辨識原始樣貌、少添加物的食物（相對於高鹽糖油的加工食品）。美國 2025–2030 飲食指南與 WHO 皆建議減少高度加工食品與添加糖攝取。" en="Whole foods are those still recognizable in their original form with few additives (vs. processed foods high in salt, sugar, and oil). Both the US 2025–2030 Dietary Guidelines and the WHO recommend cutting highly-processed foods and added sugar." />
      </p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc">
        <b><T zh="烹調法對熱量的影響（低到高）：" en="Cooking methods by calorie impact (low to high): " /></b><T zh="水煮／蒸／舒肥 → 少油快炒／烤箱 → 氣炸 → 油炸／勾芡／裹粉。氣炸並非等同水煮：澱粉類食物 &gt;130°C、蛋白質 &gt;150°C 高溫烹調可能產生丙烯醯胺／雜環胺，建議氣炸溫度控制在 160–180°C 以下。" en="boiling/steaming/sous-vide → light stir-fry/oven → air-frying → deep-frying/starch-thickening/breading. Air-frying isn't the same as boiling: starches above 130°C and proteins above 150°C can form acrylamide/heterocyclic amines — keep air-frying below 160–180°C." />
      </p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc">
        <b><T zh="備餐小技巧：" en="Meal-prep tip: " /></b><T zh="選 3 種蛋白質＋3 種碳水＋3 種油脂來源，一次批量烹煮、當週混搭，減少每日決策疲勞；冷藏建議 4 天內食用完畢，多餘份量冷凍保存。" en="pick 3 protein + 3 carb + 3 fat sources, batch-cook once, and mix through the week to cut daily decision fatigue; eat refrigerated portions within 4 days and freeze the rest." />
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Sports supplements -->
    <section class="calc-section">
      <p class="section-heading">7. <T zh="運動營養補充劑" en="Sports Supplements" /></p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc">
        <T zh="依 ISSN（國際運動營養學會）的實證等級分類：" en="Classified by the ISSN evidence tiers: " /><b>Category I</b> <T zh="證據充分支持；" en="strong support; " /><b>Category II</b> <T zh="證據有限／不一致；" en="limited/mixed; " /><b>Category III</b> <T zh="證據不足或無效。補充劑無法取代足夠的整體飲食與訓練，僅為輔助工具。" en="insufficient or ineffective. Supplements can't replace adequate overall diet and training — they're only aids." />
      </p>
      <div class="supp-table-wrap">
        <table class="supp-table">
          <thead><tr><th><T zh="補充劑" en="Supplement" /></th><th><T zh="ISSN 等級" en="ISSN tier" /></th><th><T zh="有效劑量" en="Effective dose" /></th><th><T zh="誠實結論" en="Honest verdict" /></th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
