              <td class="supp-tier tier-1">I</td>
              <td><T zh="20–40g／次，每 3–4 小時一次" en="20–40 g/serving, every 3–4 hours" /></td>
              <td><T zh="本工具蛋白質目標已依此設計；「合成代謝窗口」沒有想像中嚴格，整日總量與分次攝取比精準時機更重要。" en="This tool's protein targets follow this; the 'anabolic window' is less strict than believed — total daily intake and even distribution matter more than exact timing." /></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><T zh="肌酸 Creatine" en="Creatine" /><br><span class="supp-sub"><T zh="一水肌酸" en="Monohydrate" /></span></td>
              <td class="supp-tier tier-1">I</td>
              <td><T zh="維持期 3–5g／天（免負荷法約 3–4 週見效）" en="Maintenance 3–5 g/day (no-load method takes ~3–4 weeks)" /></td>
              <td><T zh="目前最多研究支持的合法運動營養補充劑；健康人腎功能無害為實證共識，但已有腎臟疾病者仍應諮詢醫師。" en="The most research-backed legal sports supplement; harmless to kidney function in healthy people by consensus, but those with existing kidney disease should consult a physician." /></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><T zh="咖啡因 Caffeine" en="Caffeine" /></td>
              <td class="supp-tier tier-1">I</td>
              <td><T zh="3–6 mg/kg，運動前約 60 分鐘" en="3–6 mg/kg, ~60 min before exercise" /></td>
              <td><T zh="證據最紮實的增補劑之一，效果因個人耐受度差異大。" en="One of the best-supported ergogenic aids; effect varies widely by individual tolerance." /></td>
