              <td><T zh="4–6g／天，需連續補充 2–4 週才有效果" en="4–6 g/day; needs 2–4 weeks of continuous use to work" /></td>
              <td><T zh="刺痛感是無害的副作用；非「即效型」，需要負荷期。" en="The tingling is a harmless side effect; not fast-acting — needs a loading period." /></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Citrulline malate</td>
              <td class="supp-tier tier-2">II</td>
              <td><T zh="6–8g，運動前 45–60 分鐘" en="6–8 g, 45–60 min before exercise" /></td>
