        <li>Areta JL, et al. (2013). Timing and distribution of protein ingestion during prolonged recovery from resistance exercise alters myofibrillar protein synthesis. <em>J Physiol.</em> <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC3650697/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><T zh="連結" en="link" /></a></li>
        <li>Moro T, et al. (2016). Effects of eight weeks of time-restricted feeding (16/8) on basal metabolism, maximal strength, body composition, inflammation, and cardiovascular risk factors in resistance-trained males. <em>J Transl Med.</em> <T zh="16:8 效益與睪固酮/IGF-1 下降之依據。" en="Basis for the 16:8 benefits and testosterone/IGF-1 decline. " /><a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC5064803/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><T zh="連結" en="link" /></a></li>
        <li>Time-restricted eating + resistance training <T zh="統合分析" en="meta-analysis" /> (2024). <em>Nutrients.</em> <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC11434652/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><T zh="連結" en="link" /></a></li>
        <li><T zh="外食技巧、原型食物定義為業界／營養師實務共識整理，非一手文獻回顧，僅供參考。" en="Eating-out tips and the whole-food definition are practical dietitian/industry consensus, not a primary-literature review — for reference only." /></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="calc-changelog">
        <T zh="本工具重新檢視並更新了原先 Excel 試算表中，部分取自計算機網站／部落格而非一手文獻的數值（如蛋白質與碳循環的每公斤攝取量），並修正了活動量倍率重複平均、飲食類型比例表不一致等問題。訓練排程功能已由「碳循環飲食」單一選項，擴展為適用於所有飲食類型的每週碳水調整機制。詳見 PR 說明。" en="This tool re-examined and updated values in the original Excel spreadsheet that were drawn from calculator sites/blogs rather than primary literature (e.g. protein and carb-cycling g/kg), and fixed issues like double-averaged activity multipliers and inconsistent diet-ratio tables. The training-schedule feature was expanded from a single 'carb cycling' option into a weekly carb-adjustment mechanism for all diet types. See the PR for details." />
