    <!-- Glossary -->
    <section class="calc-section">
      <p class="section-heading">9. <T zh="常見名詞解釋" en="Glossary" /></p>
      <div class="glossary-grid">
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="BMR（基礎代謝率）" en="BMR (Basal Metabolic Rate)" /></b><T zh="身體在完全靜止、清醒狀態下維持生命所需的最低熱量。" en="The minimum calories needed to sustain life at complete rest while awake." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="TDEE（每日總消耗熱量）" en="TDEE (Total Daily Energy Expenditure)" /></b><T zh="BMR 加上日常活動與運動消耗的熱量，等於「不增不減體重」所需的每日總熱量。" en="BMR plus calories burned through daily activity and exercise — the daily total needed to maintain weight." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="PAL（活動量倍率）" en="PAL (Physical Activity Level)" /></b><T zh="依生活型態估算的 BMR 乘數，用來從 BMR 推算 TDEE。" en="A BMR multiplier based on lifestyle, used to estimate TDEE from BMR." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="Mifflin-St Jeor 公式" en="Mifflin-St Jeor equation" /></b><T zh="1990 年提出，以體重、身高、年齡估算 BMR，文獻實證最準確，美國營養與飲食學會正式推薦。" en="Introduced 1990; estimates BMR from weight, height, and age. Most accurate per literature and formally recommended by the Academy of Nutrition and Dietetics." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="Katch-McArdle 公式" en="Katch-McArdle equation" /></b><T zh="以「除脂體重（LBM）」估算 BMR，體脂率越準確、估算越準，適合已知精確體脂率者。" en="Estimates BMR from lean body mass (LBM); more accurate when body fat % is known precisely." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="Harris-Benedict 公式（修訂版）" en="Harris-Benedict equation (revised)" /></b><T zh="1984 年修訂版，最早被廣泛使用的 BMR 公式之一，但對過重／肥胖者容易高估，本工具僅列為參考。" en="1984 revision; one of the earliest widely-used BMR equations, but tends to overestimate for overweight/obese people — reference only here." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="LBM（除脂體重）" en="LBM (Lean Body Mass)" /></b><T zh="體重扣除脂肪重量後的重量，包含肌肉、骨骼、器官與水分。" en="Body weight minus fat mass — includes muscle, bone, organs, and water." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="BMI（身體質量指數）" en="BMI (Body Mass Index)" /></b><T zh="體重(kg) ÷ 身高(m)²，常用體位篩檢指標，但無法區分肌肉與脂肪。" en="Weight(kg) ÷ height(m)²; a common screening index that can't distinguish muscle from fat." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="LDL（低密度脂蛋白膽固醇）" en="LDL cholesterol" /></b><T zh="俗稱「壞膽固醇」，過高與心血管疾病風險上升有關。" en="'Bad cholesterol'; high levels are linked to higher cardiovascular risk." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="HDL（高密度脂蛋白膽固醇）" en="HDL cholesterol" /></b><T zh="俗稱「好膽固醇」，具保護心血管作用，數值越高越好。" en="'Good cholesterol'; protects the cardiovascular system — higher is better." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="AMDR（巨量營養素可接受範圍）" en="AMDR" /></b><T zh="Acceptable Macronutrient Distribution Range — 官方建議的三大營養素熱量佔比範圍。" en="Acceptable Macronutrient Distribution Range — the official recommended calorie-share range for the three macros." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b>RDA／EAR</b><T zh="Recommended Dietary Allowance／Estimated Average Requirement（建議攝取量／平均需要量）— 官方營養素攝取建議的兩種標準。" en="Recommended Dietary Allowance / Estimated Average Requirement — two standards for official nutrient-intake recommendations." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="DRIs（膳食營養素參考攝取量）" en="DRIs" /></b><T zh="Dietary Reference Intakes — 台灣衛福部制定的整套營養素攝取建議標準，本工具的主要文獻依據。" en="Dietary Reference Intakes — Taiwan HPA's full set of nutrient-intake standards; this tool's primary reference." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="ACSM（美國運動醫學會）" en="ACSM" /></b><T zh="American College of Sports Medicine — 制定運動前健康篩檢與運動處方指引的權威機構。" en="American College of Sports Medicine — the authority on pre-exercise screening and exercise-prescription guidelines." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="ISSN（國際運動營養學會）" en="ISSN" /></b><T zh="International Society of Sports Nutrition — 制定蛋白質與運動營養實證建議的專業學會。" en="International Society of Sports Nutrition — the society behind evidence-based protein and sports-nutrition recommendations." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="碳循環（Carb Cycling）" en="Carb Cycling" /></b><T zh="依訓練強度每日調整碳水攝取量的飲食策略，訓練日碳水較高、休息日較低。" en="A strategy that adjusts daily carb intake by training intensity — more on training days, less on rest days." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="MHR（最大心跳率）" en="MHR (Maximum Heart Rate)" /></b><T zh="估算運動強度區間的基準心跳率，常用 220−年齡或 208−0.7×年齡估算。" en="A baseline heart rate for gauging exercise-intensity zones, commonly estimated as 220−age or 208−0.7×age." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="BUN（血中尿素氮）" en="BUN (Blood Urea Nitrogen)" /></b><T zh="血液中蛋白質代謝廢物濃度，正常參考範圍約 6–24 mg/dL；數值偏高可能反映腎臟排除廢物的能力下降。" en="Concentration of protein-metabolism waste in blood; normal ~6–24 mg/dL. High values may reflect reduced kidney waste-clearance." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="eGFR（估計腎絲球過濾率）" en="eGFR" /></b><T zh="Estimated Glomerular Filtration Rate — 估算腎臟每分鐘過濾血液的效率（mL/min/1.73m²），≥90 為正常，60–89 為輕度下降，是評估腎功能最常用的指標。" en="Estimated Glomerular Filtration Rate — how efficiently kidneys filter blood per minute (mL/min/1.73m²); ≥90 normal, 60–89 mild decline. The most common kidney-function indicator." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="GOT／AST（麩草醋酸轉氨酶）" en="GOT / AST" /></b><T zh="Glutamic-Oxaloacetic Transaminase，也稱 AST — 肝細胞受損時釋出的酵素，但也存在於心肌、骨骼肌等組織，特異性低於 GPT。" en="Glutamic-Oxaloacetic Transaminase (AST) — an enzyme released when liver cells are damaged, but also present in heart and skeletal muscle, so less liver-specific than GPT." /></div>
        <div class="glossary-item"><b><T zh="GPT／ALT（麩丙酮酸轉氨酶）" en="GPT / ALT" /></b><T zh="Glutamic-Pyruvic Transaminase，也稱 ALT — 主要存在於肝細胞，對肝臟損傷的特異性較 GOT 高，常與 GOT 一併檢驗評估肝功能。" en="Glutamic-Pyruvic Transaminase (ALT) — mainly in liver cells, more liver-specific than GOT; usually tested alongside GOT to assess liver function." /></div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

